The energy conversion technique using the solar energy is classified into two; The one is photovoltaics in which an electron–hole pair created by an incident photon is separated by an internal electric field at the p\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
